article_title: R.I. health insurance chief OKs lower rate increases for 2015
article_text:
R.I. health insurance chief OKs lower rate increases for 2015

CRANSTON — Rhode Island’s health insurance commissioner has approved premium increases for next year that are lower than those requested by most insurers and in most cases are in the single digits.The...
